import React from 'react'; import {Link, useHistory} from 'react-router-dom'; import axios from "axios"; import {connect} from "react-redux"; import loginSuccess from '/store/auth/action'; const FormAccountSettings = ({loginSuccess}) => { const history = useHistory(); const onFinish = async (values) => { try { const res = await axios.post('https://paragraf.uz/wp-json/wc/v3/user/register', values); localStorage.setItem('token', res.data.token); axios.defaults.headers['Authorization'] = `Bearer ${res.data.token}` loginSuccess(res.data); history.push('/home'); } catch (e) { } } const onFinishFailed = (errorInfo) => { console.log('Failed:', errorInfo); }; return (
); }; const mapDispatchToProps = { loginSuccess } export default connect(null, mapDispatchToProps)(FormAccountSettings);
